<!-- Game Cheats Sectional -->

<table border="0" width="100%" id="table16" cellpadding="0">
	<tr>
		<td style="font-family: Trebuchet MS; font-size: 8pt; color: #FFFFFF; font-weight: bold; text-align: left; background-color: #333333; border-left: 2px solid #000000; border-right: 2px solid #FFFFFF; border-top: 2px solid #000000; border-bottom: 2px solid #FFFFFF">
                  <br>&nbsp;<u><i><font color="#FFFF00">MISC CODES:</font></i></u><br>
                  &nbsp; Easy Capture -
			<font color="#00FF00">&nbsp;Crawl up to the monkey that you want to catch, when in crawling position swing your net at the monkey. The monkey won't notice you coming providing Easy Capture.</font>
                  <br>&nbsp; Easy Lives -
			<font color="#00FF00">&nbsp;Instead of using your stun club to kill the big robot in the level city park, make the robot come and run to the little wall on the right side, and take out your RC car and the robot should be shooting a ball of electricity but if you stay on the right you won't get hit. send your RC car right in front of the robot but not too close and it should blow up hurt him and just keep sending your RC car until it dies then there will be a life there then exit the level and re-enter for another life.</font>
                  <br>&nbsp; Rear-view Mirror -
			<font color="#00FF00">&nbsp;During the Ski mini-game, press the L1 and R1 buttons to get a rear-view mirror.</font>
                  <br>&nbsp; How to get Magic Punch -
			<font color="#00FF00">&nbsp;You get the MAGIC PUNCH after you finish the level SPECTER LAND and go back into a level with monkeys you have not caught.</font>
<br>
                  <br>&nbsp;<u><i><font color="#FFFF00">GAMESHARK CODES:</font></i></u><br>
                  &nbsp; Infinite HP -
                  <font color="#00FF00">&nbsp;<br>800EC268 0005</font>
                  <br>&nbsp; Infinite Oxygen -
                  <font color="#00FF00">&nbsp;<br>800F4D68 0258</font>
                  <br>&nbsp; Infinite Lives -
                  <font color="#00FF00">&nbsp;<br>300F442C 0005</font><br><br>
&nbsp;<br>
</td>
	 </tr>
	</table>
